-- SEC charges Mark Cuban over Mamma.com share sale
-- 
-- Mon Nov 17, 2008 12:13pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/11/17/us-cuban-idUSTRE4AG57Z20081117

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - The SEC says it has charged Mark Cuban with insider trading in shares of Mamma.com 

 Highlights: * U.S. SEC alleges Cuban sold 600,000 shares of Mamma.com on basis of nonpublic information about a stock offering * U.S. SEC charges Cuban avoided losses in excess of $750,000 by selling stock before public announcement * U.S. SEC seeks disgorgement, financial penalty